Limit is 2.8 A typical.\",\"conditions\":\"high-side peak current limit\"},{\"kind\":\"typical_current_a\",\"currentA\":3.2,\"direction\":\"unknown\",\"scope\":\"load_path\",\"basis\":\"datasheet\",\"confidence\":\"high\",\"evidence\":\"Low-Side Valley Current Limit is 3.2 A typical.\",\"conditions\":\"low-side valley current limit\"}]}},\"notes\":[\"No directly supported current facts were provided for FB, GND, or BST in the retrieved datasheet material.\",\"The EN pin note states an internal 1.5 µA pull-up current source and a 4 µA hysteresis current source, but these were not emitted as separate operating-current facts because the retrieved material presented them only as descriptive note values.\"]}"
